{"tid":2356593,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"新聞系零收生既珠海學院  環球傳播文學碩士課程現正火熱招生中！","createTime":"2021-01-07T01:49:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T03:43:37.000Z","uid":293018,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b3bfa9ca3ecb3437180c68cf5a187817e537ec9d","tid":2356593,"uid":293018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T01:49:46.000Z","msg":"上支網見到，真係好想報：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iKFu7KW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiKFu7KW.png&h=89ccf042&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">珠海學院(Chu Hai College of Higher Education)  ，位於香港新界屯門青山公路青山灣段八十號，是香港一所具有學士、碩士學位頒授資格的認可專上學院。珠海學院為香港歷史最悠久私立大專院校。<br />\n珠海新聞及傳播學系，創立於一九六八年，是香港專上院校中最早提供新聞教育的高等院校之一。歷年來系內人才輩出，在香港新聞界屢獲行內廣泛好評。本系一向師資優良，廣納資深業界及具有國內外碩士丶博士學位之學者任教。同時系內亦置有先進的硬體製作設備，以培養跨媒體領域、理論與實務兼備、全方位的媒介人才。</span><br />\n<strong>新聞系要求咁高，唔怪得今年本科零收生!! 原來係冇人有資格入!!</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x0DwBDm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx0DwBDm.png&h=40cf0799&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">現推出「環球傳播文學碩士課程」，教授在新媒體時代下以全球傳播為主軸的跨學科知識，還提供前往美國CNN學習機會，正在火熱招生中！有意往環球傳播方向深造的同學不要錯過！</span><br />\n<strong>嘩，好想讀，有得去cnn!!</strong><br />\n<br />\n睇真d....「如因疫情及各種問題不能到CNN總部，我們將另行安排計劃予同學完成有關學分，敬請留意。」 <br />\n唔緊要，我比較想去CCTV! 祖國防疫咁好，北京去得啦掛!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3fjGYRM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3fjGYRM.png&h=c7a94361&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n間學校仲咁多外國人，好國際化!! <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wrLODR6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwrLODR6.png&h=85a7ef04&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n珠海學術排名未必係香港第一，但人均面積絕對數一數二！<br />\n<br />\n真係見到都濕晒，好想衝去讀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7297f5ce8b792344b0375e1e51ab9a8419bbeb8e","tid":2356593,"uid":242537,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T01:53:35.000Z","msg":"唔係係珠海既咩<br />\n日本城係日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92008bbfc4a93b099005af8762d7f12749d5956a","tid":2356593,"uid":129042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T03:43:37.000Z","msg":"2012年個陣已經話會升格大學<br />\n啱啱瞓醒 想知升左未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}